# S3 lifecycle & cost

## Lifecycle rules

Move + delete objects by **age**, scoped to bucket / prefix / tag / size. Transitions go **downward only** (Standard → IA → Glacier); **30-day min** before IA.

- **Expire current** — retention cap
- **Expire non-current** — makes versioned buckets affordable
- **Delete expired delete markers** · **abort incomplete multipart** (silent leak)

## Cost / effort tools

- **S3 Select** — **SQL against one object** server-side → read only matching rows
- **Batch Operations** — one action over **billions** of objects (Inventory manifest)
- **Storage Lens** — org-wide dashboard + cost recommendations

**Toolkit:** lifecycle to tier/expire · Select to read less · Storage Lens to find waste.
